{
  "text": "The knowledge of the exact material characteristics of the pipes embedded in the test eld allowed us to con rm the dependence of the polarisation of the wave re ected from the material of the pipes. The Mala system recorded positive values of amplitudes of the signal re ected from the steel pipes, and negative values for the PVC pipes [CITATION_1] . The reverse polarity was demonstrated by the signal emitted by the antennas of the DS2000 system (Fig. 8) . ",
